    public abstract class BeamSqlExpression
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    BeamSqlExpression is an equivalent expression in BeamSQL, of RexNode in Calcite.

    An implementation of BeamSqlExpression takes one or more BeamSqlExpression as its operands, and return a value with type SqlTypeName.
